text: André Sødlund (born 22 January 1996 i Växjö) is a Norwegian footballer. Sødlund, who is midfielder, plays for Sandnes Ulf in the Norwegian First Division.André Sødlund, profile on soccerway.com. Sødlund arrived at Sandefjord ahead of the 2014 season after an unsuccessful spell at the Bolton Wanderers Academy.
